list.item:
(A) a decision as to what the basic nature and
                        concept of our relationship to Latin America should
                        be;

div.p:
a) seek to continue to control events as much as possible
                    within our Western hemisphere “sphere of influence”, assuming major
                    responsibility for the outcome;

b) withdraw gradually from this degree of special
                        responsibility, moving toward normal diplomatic and economic relations
                    more analogous to those we have with Africa and most of Asia;
